{"tid":1928451,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稅務局確定《印花税條例》涵蓋同性婚姻　同性伴侶享印花稅減免","createTime":"2020-03-16T11:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T14:30:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8d1e19a5d933d10abc8b92538c0ade9238276c61","tid":1928451,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"高級入境事務主任梁鎮罡去年 6 月於同性配偶福利案中獲得終極勝訴，終審法院裁定公務員同性配偶可以享有已婚公務員福利和合併報稅，公務員事務局及稅務局隨後表示會徵詢律政司意見，再作出適當的跟進。時隔九月後，稅務局近日在一封信件中確定，《印花税條例》中的婚姻定義包括同性婚姻，任何地方合法結婚的同性伴侶，均可以申請減免住宅物業交易中的買家印花稅、額外印花稅及從價印花稅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/lgbtq/%E7%A8%85%E5%8B%99%E5%B1%80%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A-%E5%8D%B0%E8%8A%B1%E7%A8%8E%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%B6%B5%E8%93%8B%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E5%A9%9A%E5%A7%BB-%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E4%BC%B4%E4%BE%B6%E4%BA%AB%E5%8D%B0%E8%8A%B1%E7%A8%85%E6%B8%9B%E5%85%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Flgbtq%2F%25E7%25A8%2585%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A-%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%25A8%258E%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%25B6%25B5%25E8%2593%258B%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%25A9%259A%25E5%25A7%25BB-%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E4%25BE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%25A8%2585%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%2585%258D%2F&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=2b1f47f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Flgbtq%2F%25E7%25A8%2585%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A-%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%25A8%258E%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%25B6%25B5%25E8%2593%258B%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%25A9%259A%25E5%25A7%25BB-%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E4%25BE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%25A8%2585%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%2585%258D%2F&h=a13ba568\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/lgbtq/%E7%A8%85%E5%8B%99%E5%B1%80%E7%A2%B